phrases: Somebody!
Is not there anyone around?!
Whoa!
What is going on, Ms. Kyoko?
Ichijo, huh?
Where are the other students?
Everyone is gone home for the day.
I am the last one.
Whaaat?
So I was too late.
Hey, I know!
All right, Ichijo, do something for me.
You look like the kind of guy who has a lot of friends.
The thing is, see, I was supposed to pick some students to clean the pool,
but it totally slipped my mind.
And so you see, Ichijo...
Tomorrow, Saturday, round up some friends and clean the pool, will you?
Whaaat?
Hold up!
Why does it have to be me?!
I am begging you, Ichijo!
I am in a real bind here!
I am always, always taking care of those animals on holidays, are not I?
So the least you can do is return the favor!
Well...
All right, I am counting on you!
The rest is up to you!
Cleanup Day
So?
You were at the end of your rope, so you came crying to me?
You really are a handful for a bean sprout!
I owe you big time.
But you know what, cleaning the pool sounds kind of exciting to me!
Sounds fun!
Talk about thinking positive...
Who else did you ask?
The thing is...
Basically, I called on the guys,
but aside from this one they all turned me down.
Looking forward to this, Kirisaki!
Do not you have any friends?
If you would said some girls' names, they all would have come running.
Like I could take advantage like that.
Ichijo!
Sorry to keep you waiting!
I am looking forward to working with you today!
Onodera...
Hey, thanks for coming!
Huh?
Who is this girl?
How do you do?
I am Haru's friend.
Haru calls me Fuu-chan.
What are you doing here?
Now, now...
You came, too, Haru?
You are so cute!
Did you really think it would be so easy?
You are not getting anywhere near my sister!
Of course I am not.
Young Mistress!
Sorry to keep you waiting!
Getting changed into this held me up.
Morning, Tsugumi!
Hey, that looks great on you!
Did not you have anything that was not quite this sparse?
I know I should not say that when you are lending this to me.
Hey, so you came, too?
It is Paula-chan, right?
Do not give me that chan treatment - it is creepy.
I am here because the Black Tiger summoned me.
Young Mistress Chitoge?
I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
I am Paula McCoy of the Beehive Hitman Team.
I have offered my life and pledged my fealty to the organization.
Should you need anything, please feel free to let me know.
Y-Yes... N-Nice to meet you.
What do you want me to do, Black Tiger?
First, let us inspect the equipment.
Master Raku!
I have missed you so
Whatever do you think you are doing, Kirisaki?
I can read you a mile away!
I guess we are all here, then.
You guys, thanks for coming today.
Once we are done, we are free to have fun as we want,
so let us get this over with as soon as we can!
Right!
Take that!
Take that!
If I could just turn all this into a DVD, I bet I would make a killing...
Forget it.
These are all people you definitely would not want as enemies.
Let us dig in!
Wow!
Looks yummy!
This is sooo good!
Did you make all this yourself, Haru?
Well, I did leave the presentation to my sister.
My intent was to whip up a conventional meal,
but before I knew it they would become posh box lunches.
Alchemy!
Paula!
Are not you going to eat with us?
Would you mind setting some aside for her?
I will hand it to her later.
All righty, how should I go about provoking the Black Tiger next?
Shall l toss that boy into the girls' locker room, maybe?
Whoops-a-daisy...
Hey... what do you think you are doing?
That is dangerous!
But you climbed up here, too, Paula.
And besides, I thought I would enjoy my lunch more if I ate it up here.
Here you go!
This is your share, Paula!
I do not want it.
But it turned out so tasty!
What is this girl's problem?
Hey, Paula, you are always looking at Tsugumi, are not you?
What is your relationship to Tsugumi?
Oh, did you go to the same junior high, maybe?
That is none of your business!
Well, you see, I have got an older sister.
See, over there!
My sister's name is Kosaki,
and she is always been sweet and a little ditzy, but she is really dependable,
and she is my beloved, precious big sister!
I was wondering if maybe you felt the same way towards Tsugumi, you know?
I told you, it is none of your business!
Why are you paying so much attention to me, anyway?!
What is the problem?
You are so stingy!
Everybody's starting to jump into the pool!
Young Mistress!
You forgot to stretch!
Why do not we go in, too, Paula?
We have got floats and water pistols and stuff!
Do whatever you want.
Hold up!
No way!
Amazing!
Jeez, talk about acting too buddy-buddy.
What do I care about relationships?
They are sure handling those water pistols like amateurs.
If it were me, I would go like...
What the...?
What is the big idea, damn you?!
No, what do you think you are doing?
It is so obvious that you are dying to join in.
If you want to play, then just play.
What... Wh-Who wants to...?
I have absolutely no desire to play!
Dummy, you cannot hide it.
It is written all over your face.
Did not you say you were trying to learn more about this world?
But I do not have a clue...
I have never played with so many people like this,
and I have no idea what expression I should have when I join in.
Idiot!
Who cares what your expression is - if you do not join in, you will never know!
You do have some interest in why Tsugumi changed after coming here, right?
Then come on.
Everybody's waiting.
Paula!
Thank goodness, you came back!
Hey, hey, want to swim together?
You are not going to swim?
Just let me make one thing clear.
I am not here because you told me to come.
I just felt like taking a break, that is all.
Yeah, sure, gotcha.
Come on, come on, do not be shy!
Let us swim!
I told you, I...
M-My legs...
Paula... you cannot swim?
Oh, shut up!
You got a problem with that?!
Whaaat?
No way!
Who knew?
So you do have some endearing aspects!
Shut up!
Shut up!
I am never getting into the pool again!
Hey, do not be like that, all right?
How anyone finds this fun, I will never know!
Jeez, I am so wiped!
Youth, eh?
Visiting the Sick
Onodera's got a cold?
That is right.
I want to go see her myself, but I have got something to do.
Ichijo, would you mind going in my place?
But are you sure it is okay for me to go?
What are you talking about?
Kosaki says she wants you to come over.
Whaaat?
ONODERA JAPANESE CONFECTIONS
And so I did end up coming,
but is it really okay?
A guy visiting a girl at home alone?
Closed for the next few days
Huh?
The shop is closed.
Come to think of it, Miyamoto did tell me to go in from the back.
Yes?
Yes?
Who is there...?
Huh?
Wait... Onodera?
What is wrong, Onodera?
Open up, will you?
Okay?
Come on!
I-Ichijo... what are you doing here?
Well...
Miyamoto said she had an errand to run, so I am here in her place.
She never said anything to me!
What the hell, Miyamoto?
Giving me false hope!
Thanks to you, I have come to see her, but...
Hey...
My fever's going to spike!
All right...
All right, why do not you come in for now?
Are you sure?
How are you feeling?
Yes, it is fine.
I still have a fever, but I have got some medicine.
Come to think of it, the shop's closed today.
Yes, the thing is, Mom's away on a trip with her friends from the shopping arcade.
She will not be back for another few days.
What?
Meaning that...
could it be that today I am here alone with Onodera?
Hello?
Is this the police?
There is a prowler inside my home!
Hold up, hold up, hold up!
Who are you calling a prowler?
What are you doing here in our home, Senpai?!
Just get out of here right now!
Hey, Haru!
Ichijo came here to check up on me, you know?
You should not be rude to him!
But there is no need.
For him to check on you.
You have got me at your side, Sister.
All right, Senpai, thank you for coming over!
There is nothing to worry about anymore!
Hold up, hold up, Haru!
Uh...
If you like...
Here!
You did tell me that you loved the strawberry rice cakes from Suzumiya.
Dangling a carrot in front of me... did you really think that would work?
Well, I guess I will let you stay for a little while, but...
Thanks.
Then would you mind if I borrowed your kitchen?
I would like to make some rice gruel or something.
You do not have to do that.
Oh, then I will give you a hand.
Sister, you rest up, all right?
So...
What are you plotting, anyway?
Are you planning to take advantage of my sister when she is vulnerable?
I am not plotting anything.
I find that very hard to believe.
Coming here when you already have a girlfriend...
will not that gorgeous girlfriend of yours be pissed?
Well, it is...
It is really complicated, you see...
How interesting.
A situation where you are allowed to be a two-timer?
What could that be?
It is no good.
Far from being alone with Onodera, it does not look like I can even have a nice talk with her.
Could it be that you are after that locket?
I am not handing it over.
I am going to give that back to my prince myself!
No, although I do admit I want it back.
Do not let your guard down, Haru.
Now that Sister's so vulnerable, I have got to protect her!
Sister!
Your rice gruel is read
Why are you cleaning up, Sister?
Come on!
You are sick, so you have got to stay in bed!
I could not help it.
Who knew that I would ever get to enter this room again.
Here, Sister, we made you some rice gruel.
Have it!
Okay.
Sister?
All right, say ahhh!
It is all right, I can eat on my own.
What do you say?
Are not you jealous?
Th-This kid!
Um...
Yeah, I think your fever totally broke.
Looks like you are going to be all right!
All right, Sister, drink lots of water and get lots of rest.
Just call me on my cell phone, and I will come anytime!
Right.
Come on!
Let us go, Senpai!
I know, I know!
Huh?
But I am still running a temperature.
All right, there is nothing else you can help out with, Senpai.
Why do not you take your leave now?
Sorry, Haru.
Hey!
What are you doing, all of a sudden?!
That was totally sexual harassment!
Haru, you have caught Onodera's cold, right?
I-I did not catch it.
As you can see, I am fit as a fiddle...
Go to bed!
No!
If I collapse, too, what is going to become of my sister?!
I do not have any plans today,
so I could look after her, if that is okay.
Why would it be okay?!
Something like that!
If it means leaving my sister in your care,
I would rather just pass out myself!
Hey, that is enough!
If you were to push yourself too hard and collapse,
who would end up feeling the most responsible?!
Hey, I do not want to make Onodera feel uncomfortable, either,
and I do not intend to.
And I do not have the guts to do what you are so worried I will.
Understood.
Seriously...
Pushing herself so irrationally for someone else's sake...
I can see that she is Onodera's kid sister, all right.
Coming in!
Haru,
you still have not eaten, have you?
I did make you some rice gruel.
I do not want it, really.
It is not like I have any appetite.
Come on, do not be so stubborn.
You need to eat while you can.
Or is it something else?
Want me to feed you like you did Onodera?
Here... ahhh...
Sorry, I should not have done that.
I just have to eat it, right?
Right?
Yummy!
Well?
Is it good?
What is this?
It was not the least bit good!
You cannot even make a decent rice gruel.
Your ineptitude is enough to make me drool!
Oh, is that right?
All right, I am going to leave this drink here,
so be sure to keep sipping it and get some rest, okay?
See you.
What is up with that?
Pretending to be a gentleman...
When he does not give a second thought about two-timing.
Well, but that rice gruel was good.
My body feels so hot.
I was all tensed up till now...
so the fatigue just hit me at once.
I think...
I am in agony...
What is this?
Something cold on my forehead.
It feels so good.
When did I fall asleep...?
I-Ichijo-senpai!
What are you doing sleeping here?
A cold compress?
Is that what felt so good?
Have you been changing them all this time?
For me?
But why?
This guy...
He is not the kind of person to do such a...
He is really gentle, you know...
Ichijo.
Whoa, my bad!
I must have nodded off.
Who knew I would fall asleep here?
It is all right, do not worry!
I swear I did not do anything to you!
So everything's fine, okay?
Hey, that is right,
how is your fever?
Yes, thanks to you, it came down a lot.
Is that right?
Thank goodness.
Hey!
Not good!
I have got to go change Onodera's compress, too.
Whoa...
Whoops, whoops, whoops!
Oh, crap, I went and did it!
My bad, I will pick that up right now!
Wh-What is so funny?
Well, but Ichijo-senpai,
you are somehow even weirder than I thought!
You have not smiled at me like that since we first met in the hallway.
Wh-What is that supposed to mean?
Is there a problem?
No... there is no problem.
Ichijo-senpai, if you please.
A lot has happened between us, but...
You are giving it back to me?
No, I am not!
I am just leaving it in your care.
When the day comes for me to be reunited with my prince,
please give it back to me.
Until then, I am granting you special custody.
But in return,
please let me see my prince again someday.
Or else I am going to stick a needle in your eye!
Right...
Roger that.
But see, that is...
I admit he is just a tiny bit different than what I thought, Sister.
